  // ground. Generated at deploy time from data/760/actions/definitions.json by
  // tools/build-usable-items.js. Best-effort: if it fails to load the set stays
  // empty and the client falls back to its own dat-flag/door/step-on detection
  // (decorations still don't walk; rare flag-less server-action items just won't
