  //              ALSO caused player-visible bugs (probably paintings + other
  //              wall-mounts that share lamp's stateful-render path). REVERTED.
  //   THIS attempt — trophy CID range ONLY (2669-2686 = SID 1882-1899).
  //   Trophies don't carry HookSouth themselves and have no animation state,
  //   so the lit-lamp ping-pong mechanism doesn't apply. Lamps + paintings
  //   are at different CIDs and untouched.
  this.items = tile.items;
